column5: I have just finished publishing another 17 articles about channel catfish and walleye on the Red an Winnipeg rivers in Manitoba Canada. Those interested can find them at my site www.geocities.com/dkiazyk2000 under the link "articles". Tight lines, DanP.S. If your interested in knowing what's going on in the keystone province, one of Manitoba's hottest fishing bulletin boards (Fishing Manitoba) has a link from my site as well.
